
<hr>
<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="title is-4">Comments</h2>
        <p>どなたでもご自由に書き込んでください。</p>
        <br>
        <p>Fully Hatter が、愛には愛で、剣には剣でご返事いたします。</p>
        <br>
        <br>
    </div>
    <form method="post" action="{{urlPath}}/comment">
        <div class="field">
            <label class="label is-small">名前</label>
            <div class="control is-small has-icons-left">
                <input class="input" type="text" name="name" placeholder="Fully Hatter" maxlength="20">
                <span class="icon is-small">
                    <figure class="image is-16x16">
                        <img src="/images/icon/person.png" alt="person logo">
                    </figure>
                </span>
            </div>
            <p class="help is-small">偽名推奨</p>
        </div>

        <div class="field">
            <label class="label is-small">コメント</label>
            <div class="control is-small">
                <textarea class="textarea" name="comment" placeholder="ご自由にどうぞ" maxlength="1000"></textarea>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="field is-grouped">
            <div class="control">
                <button class="button is-small is-link">送信</button>
            </div>
            <div class="control">
                <button class="button is-small is-text">キャンセル</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </form>
</section>
<section class="section">
    {{{comments}}}
</section>
